# Signara Design System

## Brand Palette

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `signara-navy` | `#0F2C59` | Primary brand, headings, sidebars, nav backgrounds, body text |
| `signara-gold` | `#D4AF37` | Accent, CTAs, active wizard steps, highlights, hover states, icons |
| `signara-steel` | `#A1A8A2` | Borders, secondary text, metallic UI accents, dividers |
| `signara-background` | `#F8F9FA` | Main canvas / page background |
| White | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, modals, input backgrounds |

The logo uses **deep navy** script text + a **gold/brass fountain pen nib** — every UI decision must honour this pairing.

## CSS Variables (shadcn/Tailwind layer base)

```css
@layer base {
  :root {
    --background: 210 20% 98%;        /* #F8F9FA */
    --card: 0 0% 100%;
    --popover: 0 0% 100%;
    --primary: 216 71% 20%;           /* #0F2C59 navy */
    --primary-foreground: 210 20% 98%;
    --accent: 46 65% 52%;             /* #D4AF37 gold */
    --accent-foreground: 216 71% 20%;
    --border: 129 4% 65%;             /* #A1A8A2 steel */
    --input: 129 4% 65%;
    --ring: 216 71% 20%;
    --foreground: 216 71% 20%;
    --muted: 129 4% 65%;
    --muted-foreground: 215 15% 40%;
  }
}
```

